                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>; <strong>Trigger</strong> The doppelganger is transformed with Change Shape and another creature moves adjacent to it or takes a hostile action against it. <strong>Effect</strong> The doppelganger reverts to its natural form and can make a Strike against the triggering creature. If the creature was unaware the doppelganger was in disguise, that creature is flat-footed against this attack.</p>"
